Easy Banana Bread

70 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Description

A moist and flavorful banana bread that's perfect for breakfast or a snack.

Ingredients

  • ripe bananas: 3 large
  • all-purpose flour: 1.5 cups
  • sugar: 1 cup
  • baking soda: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 0.5 teaspoon
  • butter: 0.5 cup (melted)
  • eggs: 2 large
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
